You do need to export those interface if you want that type info for intelliSense, etc:

```ts
export interface Options {
    decimals?: number;
    ...
}

export interface Instance {
    ...
}
```

You should modify the test to use these types to make sure it actually works:

```ts
const options: wNumb.Options = {decimals: 1}
const moneyFormat: wNumb.Instance = wNumb(options);
```

Otherwise your types will just show up as `any` which is probably not what you want.

